summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting a deed for street purposes to a portion of the Southeast Quarter of Section 4, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M., a portion of Lot 1, Block 3, Charles Addition to the City of Seattle, and a portion of Lots 1 and 2, Block 3, Hick's Addition to the City of Seattle, and laying off South Charles Street (RW 8960).
